title: Search Ranked Team in Silver - Prefer Top>MId>Support
body:
Hello, I search a Ranked team for Silver 5.
I main Top and Mid, also available as support if needed.
Favourite playstyle Splitpush, but also fit in pokecomps.
Main Champs: Nidalee, Cho´Gath and Trundle.
I´m male and 18 years old.
Native Language German, but speak a good english.
Mostly online between 20.00 and 22.00.
Prefer NO voice chats like Skype or TS, maybe later, but in first time no.

If interrested add Hoan97.
